section

  md-subheader(md-colors="{background: 'default-primary-hue-1'}")
    | Registration for

  //- Hero
  div.hero(layout='row', layout-xs='column', md-colors="{background: 'default-primary-hue-2'}")
    
    div(
      flex,
      layout='row',
      layout-align='center center',
      layout-padding,
      ng-show='vm.actionLoading'
    )
    
      md-progress-circular.md-background(
        ng-show='vm.actionLoading',
        md-mode='indeterminate',
        md-diameter='100px'
      )
    
    div(flex-gt-xs='50', flex-xs, layout='row', ng-hide='vm.actionLoading')
      div(flex-gt-xs='75', layout='column')
        md-content(layout-padding, md-colors="{background: 'default-primary-hue-2'}")
          div(hide, show-gt-sm)
            h1.md-display-2 Active travellers
            h2.md-display-1 keep the world healthy
          div(hide-gt-sm)
            h1.md-display-1 Active travellers
            h2.md-headline keep the world healthy
          p Kids and teachers across Australia are teaming up to help reduce our
            |  collective carbon footprint, and inspire more active travellers.
            |  By encouraging your class to walk, scoot, or cycle to and from
            |  school we can make both our planet and your school a happier,
            |  healthier place to be.
          //- div(hide, show-gt-sm)
          //-   h3.md-title Would you like to play?
          //- div(hide-gt-sm)
          //-   h3.md-title Would you like to play?
      span(hide, show-gt-xs, flex)
    div(
      flex-gt-xs='50',
      flex-xs,
      layout='row',
      layout-align='center center',
      ng-hide='vm.actionLoading'
    )
      img(
        ng-src='/images/APF-logo-main-2x.png',
        alt='Asia Pacific Forum logo'
      )
    
section(hide)
  
  //- Content
  div.content

    md-content(layout-padding, layout='row', layout-xs='column')
      
      // Help text
      div(flex-xs, flex-gt-sm='33', layout='column')
        md-card
          md-card-title
            md-card-title-text.md-headline
              | More fun
          md-card-content
            p
              | Kids love to move and have fun, but research shows they are not
              |  getting enough of their daily dose. Active travel helps kids:

      // Form
      div(flex, layout='column')
        md-card
          md-card-header
            md-card-header-text
              span.md-display-1 Personal
                a(name='personal')
            md-card-avatar
              md-icon.material-icons(md-colors="{background: 'default-accent-hue-1'}") done
        md-card
          md-card-header(md-colors="{background: 'default-accent-hue-1'}")
            md-card-header-text
              span.md-display-1 Personal
                a(name='personal')
          md-card-content
            md-input-container.md-block(flex)
              label First name
              input(ng-model='vm.student.name', name='studentName', required)
              div(ng-messages='beginForm.studentName.$error', role='alert')
                div(ng-message='required')
                  | We need to know who's playing the game
          md-card-actions(layout='row', layout-align='end center')
            md-button Previous
            md-button Next
        md-card(md-colors="{background: 'default-background-hue-3'}")
          md-card-header
            md-card-header-text
              span.md-display-1 Personal
                a(name='personal')
